      <title>欧元区通胀率跌破2%，降息可能性增强</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-inflation-dips-below-2-strengthening-rate-cut-case-2024-10-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月份，欧元区通胀率自 2021 年年中以来首次跌破 2%，这进一步证实了欧洲央行本月降息的充分理由，因为为期三年的抑制价格失控增长的斗争即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-inflation-dips-below-2-strengthening-rate-cut-case-2024-10-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 09:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
